<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5202093>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Eusparassus kronebergi Denis, 1958 stat. nov., (A–E) lectotype male from Faizabad, Sistan, Afghanistan: (A) eye arrangement; (B) left chelicera, ventral; (C) left palp, ventral; (D) left palp, retrolateral; (E) tip of embolus and conductor, ventral; (F, G) paralectotype female from Farah, Farah Province, Afghanistan: (F) epigyne; (G) left vulva, anterio-dorso-lateral. Scale bars: (A–C, E) 1 mm, (D, F) 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5202093/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

